text: Kaba Sambou (born 20 April 1996) is a Gambian international footballer who plays for Samtredia, as a midfielder. ==Career== Born in Manjai Kunda, he has played club football for Banjul Hawks, Stade de Mbour, Trepça'89, Skënderbeu Korçë and Samtredia.
